Put static app on heroku:
http://stackoverflow.com/questions/10551273/is-it-possible-to-upload-a-simple-html-and-javascript-file-structure-to-heroku


git init
git add .
git commit -m...

on github.com, create new repo without README

git remote add origin https://github.com/pgarber/RB_Design1.git
git remote -v
git push origin master

heroku apps:create rbdesign1

$git remote -v
heroku	git@heroku.com:rbdesign1.git (fetch)
heroku	git@heroku.com:rbdesign1.git (push)
origin	https://github.com/pgarber/RB_Design1.git (fetch)
origin	https://github.com/pgarber/RB_Design1.git (push)

git push heroku master
    http://rbdesign1.herokuapp.com